cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation of retinal images. Additionally, the use of analytic and geometric properties suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.AI), and the topological approach may involve graph theory (cs.GR). The use of DRIVE retinal image database may also suggest involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) and deep learning techniques.
